title: Megyn Kelly Rips Media Coverage Of Hillary Clinton Benghazi Committee Testimony
text: Megyn Kelly claims the mainstream media has ignored a bombshell revelation from the Hillary Clinton Benghazi Committee testimony in their headlong rush to declare the Democrat presidential front-runner victorious over the GOP-led inquiry led by Congressman and former prosecutor Trey Gowdy. The news media viewed the hearing through the lens of partisan politics and political...
